  IntlBackslash  1    2    3    4    5    6    7    8    9    0    -    =    bspc
  tab            q    w    e    r    t    y    u    i    o    p    [    ]
  caps           a    s    d    f    g    h    j    k    l    ;    '    \     ret
  lsft           grv  z    x    c    v    b    n    m    ,    .    /         rsft
  fn             lctl lalt lmet           spc            rmet ralt rctl      up
                                                                       left down right
)
